                <article class="editor"><p><img class="round-border" src="/upload/page/35/self/677df5862f19a.jpg" alt="Self Photos / Files - Playground" width="1060" height="1000" /></p></article>
            </div>
                            <div class="responsive">
                <article class="editor"><h3 class="homepage-title title"><span class="colour2"><strong>Our vision</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is for every child to be the best that they can be.</span></span></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="round-border" src="/upload/page/35/self/677df5862f19a.jpg" alt="Self Photos / Files - Playground" width="1063" height="1000" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="rounded_border_title"><a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/">Discover our Vision</a></p></article>
            </div>
            </div>
</section>
<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can Glenealy School offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/364eac103622cdee7b3b84e7bf4eb905.png" alt="ESF_Logomark_BW_RGB" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/marketing_family/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/71dbfac2f9bd0040c409f92947828659.png" alt="Real-world Experience" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Positive & Nurturing Relationships</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>A key motivation at Glenealy School is to cultivate a sense of belonging among all members of our community. Through our curriculum, our social experiences and our community events, we aim to facilitate open engagement with shared human values and experiences.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_wellbeing/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/19abd475835f988aa1105176cf23b6c4.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Progressive & Innovative Learning Experiences</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our pedagogical practices are used to engage children in exploring the environment around them, make connections to their world and encourage them to take action.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/18b19fd95a93a1c210663cd1e52cb9aa.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Student Centred Learning Environment</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>To nurture curious, connected collaborators, we cultivate an overall educational approach that inspires learning both inside and beyond the classroom, fostering a sense of belonging, trust, and creativity. By promoting inclusivity and connection, we create a supportive community where every student feels valued and empowered to contribute.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/7b47326cc2f8d0fe249280217dd9c7a5.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Extensive Extra Curricular Programme</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our extensive ECA programme unlocks diverse learning beyond the classroom - from performances to tournaments, enriching students with over 70 engaging experiences each year.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/extra_curricular_activities/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/adc45c176736f3a4b34b2d18cf03172e.png" alt="Strong Community Network" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong Community Partnerships</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Learning grows the more children, peers, adults & the community are connected to it. We are dedicated to cultivating strong community engagement through partnerships that forge community spirit.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/parent_partnership/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/7695575adfc8c2ae02b3caaa1e8e4a2f.jpg" alt="Untitled design" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Primary Years Programme (PYP)</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1"></button>
                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Glenealy School is proud to offer a Primary Years Programme (PYP) curriculum that provides progressive and innovative learning experiences for your children. Our curriculum is grounded in the principles of an International Baccalaureate (IB) education, which emphasizes holistic development and cultivating lifelong learners.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At Glenealy School, our PYP Programme aims to empower your children to become lifelong learners, critical thinkers, and compassionate global citizens. We invite you to join us in this exciting journey as partners in your child's education.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="section4" data-total="5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg bg-colour4"></div>
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Life at Glenealy School</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="record-slider">
            <div class="slider-container">
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/efacf087264c1e09587c9be5e22cffee.jpeg" alt="IMG_5220" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Diversity Equity Inclusivity (DEI)</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>At Glenealy, we wholeheartedly celebrate diversity, equity, and inclusion, actively embracing the evolving needs of our community. Our goal is to create learning environments where every child feels a sense of belonging and is empowered to thrive.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/e70ae8521db1e376d7736a9d47632be6.jpg" alt="20241107_112620" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Outdoor Learning</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We immerse our students in the beauty of the natural environment through engaging field trips, outdoor learning, and projects that cultivate a sense of environmental stewardship from an early age. Our adventure camps and cultural immersion trips provide transformative experiences that enhance teamwork, promote personal growth, and broaden global perspectives. These unforgettable opportunities are truly highlights of the Glenealy experience.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/outdoor_learning/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/cfd666d4c2bb5211b947cce304593eed.jpg" alt="IMG_1613" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Student Leadership</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We empower our students through leadership opportunities that allow them to express their ideas and drive positive change within our community. Our House Leaders organize events that promote teamwork and school spirit, while Student Ambassadors help connect new students and families. This engagement fosters a sense of ownership and belonging, inspiring everyone to actively participate in school life.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_people/student_voice/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/7235769076ec92b8c9595052c381c50f.jpg" alt="8dec86a7-6337-4351-a561-0659b0d82255" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>Extra-Curricular Activities</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>Our dynamic after-school program and sports teams provide over 100 diverse experiences, designed to develop skills, nurture talents, and foster collaboration with other schools. These enriching opportunities not only enhance individual growth but also promote teamwork and community engagement.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/extra_curricular_activities/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
                                    <div class="record-item">
                        <img src="/cache/img/3ee0dd1925fdc335b8ab5e704dda666b.jpg" alt="20241025_134055" loading="lazy" width="1070" height="802" />                        <div class="overlay">
                            <div class="bg-colour2"></div>
                            <h3>
                                <span>The Arts</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>We celebrate the vibrant world of creativity through both visual and performing arts. Our students are encouraged to explore and express their artistic talents in diverse ways, including painting, sculpture, music, dance, and theatre. This varied approach allows them to discover their passions and develop their unique voices in a supportive environment.</p>
                                                            <a href="https://glenealy
	.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/specialist_provision/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
                                    <span>Find out more</span>
                                </a>
                                                    </div>
                    </div>
