                                                    <h3>Marie-Louise Li - Class of 1983</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/cb31545a29bb83a3697926b722ab14ab.jpg" alt="eb" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>3 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">“As a Glenealy alumnus, it’s exciting to have sent all three of my children to the school at which I grew up, while at the same time experiencing how in the intervening years, Glenealy has transformed from strength to strength, still providing a solid foundation where each child can thrive.”</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">“As a Glenealy alumnus, it’s exciting to have sent all three of my children to the school at which I grew up, while at the same time experiencing how in the intervening years, Glenealy has transformed from strength to strength, still providing a solid foundation where each child can thrive.”</p>
