    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
            
            $('.tab', '#section6').click(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($(this).index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.tab-select', '#section6').change(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' +  ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.select .select-container div', '#section6').show();
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.record-slider', '#section6').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: true
            });

            function chkContentHeight() {
                $('p.description', '#section6').each(function() {
                    if($(this).height() > 160) {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('more');
                    }
                });
            }
            chkContentHeight();

            $('.record-item article button.view-more', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-less').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').show();
            });
            $('.record-item article button.view-less', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-more').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section7" data-total="10">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What’s new at Glenealy School?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="record-slider">
        <div class="slider-container">
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="309">
                        <time>28/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>From whipping up colorful playdough to baking delicious pineapple buns, children have been busy creating culinary magic in the kitchen! 🍍🥖✨</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/265e68042ad45b9b715d08d0f961eacf.jpg" alt="641702720_910351538030996_6496494222532044447_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="308">
                        <time>27/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Today’s assembly featured piano performances, awards for our young writers and long‑distance runners, and an update from Year 5 on their How the World Works inquiry. We also introduced safety as our word of the week, shared plans for next week’s Book Week, and learnt that Robinson and Kennedy are now tied for first after the House Quiz!</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/e8220636c6ff1e0ffac2f003904089ed.jpg" alt="643910273_909590751440408_8696829778297544185_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="307">
                        <time>27/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>🌟 We always cherish the opportunity to connect with our families! Today, we were thrilled to learn about the rich heritage of Mexican culture from one of our students' grandparents. Thank you for sharing your stories with us! 🇲🇽❤️</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d463332f4874da481f79b6ec79c27fbe.jpg" alt="641385816_909318771467606_9016785085309010205_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="306">
                        <time>26/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Today saw the Glenealy Rugby players representing us as they played against The Peak School. There were lots of try’s and wins for the Glenealy teams. Gooooo Glenealy!</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/3f68e8c4f87ac28f6241fa9ce49c648e.jpg" alt="643728158_908828984849918_5946442768495495426_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="305">
                        <time>25/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Another day, another series of hockey matches for the Glenealy hockey players. Todays games against FIS were at a more sociable time, but bore the same fabulous results as yesterdays games, with plenty of goals scored and wins for Glenealy.</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/7b2c58b45af04fe625981f91b650ff56.jpg" alt="641613422_908141181585365_7574797082738763521_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="304">
                        <time>24/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>It was an early start for the Glenealy hockey players today as they gathered at 6.45am to play a series of games against Kennedy School. Getting out of bed early was definitely worth it as they showed off their talents and won virtually all their games. Goooooo Glenealy!</h3>
